      "factId": "hz.web.e3c23ccf8a8cd492.fact.3",
      "kind": "bullet",
      "text": "For <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/manzoorwanijk/\">Manzoor Ahmad</a>, a code wrangler on Automattic’s Triforce team, paid parental leave meant time to care for his wife, support his newborn son through a difficult start, and focus on his family without the added pressure of work or lost income.</p> <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Manzoor and his wife were expecting their first child near the end of July, but the pregnancy became complicated much earlier.",
